## 🧠 Learnings

* Implemented **Authentication & Authorization** using JWT (stateless sessions with cookies)
* Understood how **JWT-based stateless authentication** works (token generation, verification, middleware protection)
* Built **role-based access control (RBAC)** to differentiate Admin and Normal users
* Designed a **clean MVC architecture** with separation of concerns (controllers, services, middleware)
* Handled **real-world edge cases** like duplicate users, invalid inputs, and API abuse (rate limiting)
* Learned how to structure a backend project for **scalability and maintainability**


